<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Learn more about HyperCar Showcase, your ultimate platform for hypercar enthusiasts."
    />
    <title>About Us - HyperCar Showcase</title>
    <style>
      /* 
        Documentation: Styles for the "About Us" page.
        - Background: Dark theme (#1a1a1a) with contrasting red highlights (#cc0000).
        - Font: Uses Arial for readability.
        - Layout: Centers main content with padding and shadows for a clean, modern design.
        */
      body {
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #1a1a1a;
        color: #fff;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      header {
        background: #cc0000;
        padding: 1rem 0;
        text-align: center;
        position: relative;
      }

      header h1 {
        margin: 0;
        color: #fff;
      }

      header img {
        height: 100px;
        width: auto;
        position: absolute;
        top: 45%;
        left: 20px;
        transform: translateY(-50%);
      }

      main {
        max-width: 900px;
        margin: 2rem auto;
        padding: 1.5rem;
        background: #cc0000;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 20px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.75);
        opacity: 0;
        animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease forwards;
      }

      h2 {
        color: black;
        margin-top: 1.5rem;
        position: relative;
        padding-left: 15px;
      }

      h2:before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        left: 0;
        top: 0;
        height: 100%;
        width: 4px;
        background: #cc0000;
        transform: scaleY(0);
        animation: scaleIn 0.5s ease forwards;
      }

      p,
      li {
        color: #ddd;
        text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
      }

      ul {
        padding-left: 20px;
      }

      footer {
        text-align: center;
        padding: 1rem;
        background: #333;
        color: #ccc;
        margin-top: 2rem;
      }

      footer a {
        color: #cc0000;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .logo-image {
        height: 100px;
        width: auto;
        position: absolute;
        top: 65%;
        left: 20px;
      }

      .home-icon {
        position: absolute;
        top: -8px;
        right: -15px;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        width: 120px;
        height: 110px;
        background-color: transparent;
        border-radius: 0%;
        text-decoration: none;
        box-shadow: none;
        z-index: 10;
      }

      .home-icon img {
        width: 80%;
        height: auto;
        display: block;
      }

      .home-icon .go-back-text {
        color: black;
        font-size: 14px;
        margin-left: 20px;
        margin-top: -20px;
        font-weight: bold;
      }

      .home-icon:hover {
        background-color: transparent;
        transform: scale(1.1);
        transition: transform 0.2s ease, background-color 0.2s ease;
      }

      /* Enhanced content animations */
      ul li {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateX(-20px);
        animation: slideInLeft 0.5s ease forwards;
      }

      /* Stagger list item animations */
      ul li:nth-child(1) {
        animation-delay: 0.2s;
      }
      ul li:nth-child(2) {
        animation-delay: 0.4s;
      }
      ul li:nth-child(3) {
        animation-delay: 0.6s;
      }
      ul li:nth-child(4) {
        animation-delay: 0.8s;
      }
      ul li:nth-child(5) {
        animation-delay: 1s;
      }

      @keyframes fadeInUp {
        from {
          opacity: 0;
          transform: translateY(30px);
        }
        to {
          opacity: 1;
          transform: translateY(0);
        }
      }

      @keyframes scaleIn {
        to {
          transform: scaleY(1);
        }
      }

      @keyframes slideInLeft {
        to {
          opacity: 1;
          transform: translateX(0);
        }
      }

      /* Enhanced paragraph styling */
      p {
        line-height: 1.8;
        position: relative;
        padding-left: 20px;
      }

      p:before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        left: 0;
        top: 50%;
        width: 8px;
        height: 8px;
        background: #cc0000;
        border-radius: 50%;
        transform: translateY(-50%);
      }

      /* Improved header animation */
      header {
        position: relative;
        overflow: hidden;
      }

      header:after {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        top: 0;
        left: -100%;
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        background: linear-gradient(
          90deg,
          transparent,
          rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2),
          transparent
        );
        animation: shine 3s infinite;
      }

      @keyframes shine {
        to {
          left: 100%;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <!-- 
    Documentation: "About Us" Page Content
    - Purpose: Displays information about the HyperCar Showcase platform.
    - Features:
      1. Header section with logo and title.
      2. Main section describing vision, offerings, and benefits.
      3. Footer with contact details.
    -->

    <header>
      <!-- Logo and Title -->
      <img
        src="/images/logo.png"
        alt="HyperCar Showcase Logo"
        class="logo-image"
      />
      <!-- Logo for the page -->
      <h1>About HyperCar Showcase</h1>

      <!-- Home Icon: Links to Homepage -->
      <a href="home" class="home-icon" title="Go to Homepage">
        <img src="/images/homeicon.png" alt="Home" />
      </a>
    </header>
    <main>
      <!-- Vision and Mission Statements -->
      <h2>About HyperCar Showcase</h2>
      <p>
        Welcome to HyperCar Showcase, the ultimate destination for hypercar
        enthusiasts who are captivated by the thrill of speed, the elegance of
        luxury, and the pursuit of automotive perfection. Here, we bring the
        world's most exclusive hypercars to your fingertips, creating an
        immersive experience like no other.
      </p>

      <h2>Our Vision</h2>
      <p>
        Our vision is to unite hypercar aficionados from around the globe
        through a platform that celebrates innovation, performance, and style.
        HyperCar Showcase is more than just a platform—it's a community where
        passion for hypercars meets cutting-edge insights and exploration.
      </p>

      <!-- Features Section -->
      <h2>Discover What We Offer</h2>
      <p>
        At HyperCar Showcase, we provide a comprehensive experience for every
        hypercar enthusiast. Dive into features designed to inspire and inform:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          Explore in-depth details and high-quality visuals of the world's most
          iconic hypercars.
        </li>
        <li>
          Compare performance metrics, technical specifications, and pricing
          effortlessly.
        </li>
        <li>
          Build your personal collection of favorite hypercars and keep them all
          in one place.
        </li>
        <li>
          Connect with other enthusiasts by reading and contributing reviews.
        </li>
        <li>
          Locate authorized service centers associated with top manufacturers.
        </li>
      </ul>

      <!-- Unique Selling Proposition -->
      <h2>Why HyperCar Showcase?</h2>
      <p>
        We blend sophistication and simplicity to deliver a showcase that truly
        reflects the world of hypercars. Our bold red and black design echoes
        the spirit of hypercar culture—sleek, powerful, and exhilarating.
        Whether you're seeking inspiration or knowledge, we ensure an experience
        that's as thrilling as the cars themselves.
      </p>

      <!-- Call to Action -->
      <h2>Join the Hypercar Lifestyle</h2>
      <p>
        HyperCar Showcase is your gateway to the world of high-performance
        automotive excellence. Whether you're a seasoned collector, a
        performance enthusiast, or someone who dreams of owning a hypercar, this
        is the place to explore, connect, and indulge in the art of driving.
        Start your journey today and immerse yourself in the pinnacle of
        automotive craftsmanship.
      </p>
    </main>

    <footer>
      <!-- Footer with Contact Details -->
      <p>
        &copy; 2024 HyperCar Showcase. All Rights Reserved. |
        <a href="https://www.instagram.com/joewrdd" target="_blank"
          >Contact Us</a
        >
      </p>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
